name: Vello Systems
overview: Vello Systems, Inc. engages in engineering, manufacturing, and marketing ultra-low latency multi-terabit cloud infrastructure systems for service providers, enterprises, and government institutions in the United States and internationally. It offers CX Family of cloud infrastructure systems that deliver low-latency multi-terabit capacity for the wide-area; and CloudMaster, an element management and provisioning system. The company also provides campus MAN/WAN, data center internetworking, virtualization infrastructure, metro-based high-frequency trading, and long-haul high-frequency trading solutions. In addition, it offers core and metro networking, data center internetworking, virtualization infrastructure, residential cloud infrastructure, commercial cloud infrastructure, and mobile cloud infrastructure solutions. Further, the company provides network and system planning, installation and commissioning, warranty, and continuous support and services. Vello Systems, Inc. was founded in 2009 and is based in Menlo Park, California.

funding_rounds.source_description: Vello Systems Scores $25M To Continue Enterprise Networking Push
